{"id":4186,"date":"2025-06-16T14:09:50","date_gmt":"2025-06-16T07:09:50","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?p=4186"},"modified":"2025-06-16T14:09:50","modified_gmt":"2025-06-16T07:09:50","slug":"mang-loc-chong-nang","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/thong-tin-nganh\/mang-loc-chong-nang\/","title":{"rendered":"M\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng l\u00e0 g\u00ec? Hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn kem b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Khi nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng cho da \u0111ang treatment, y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 then ch\u1ed1t quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 n\u1eb1m \u1edf ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 SPF hay PA, m\u00e0 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 <\/span><b>m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> &#8220;h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o&#8221; \u00e2m th\u1ea7m nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng thi\u1ebft y\u1ebfu. V\u1eady c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0y ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o? C\u00f3 bao nhi\u00eau lo\u1ea1i? V\u00e0 b\u1ea1n n\u00ean l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ra sao?<\/span><\/p>\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"co-che-hoat-dong-cua-cac-mang-loc-trong-kem-chong-nang\"><\/span><b>C\u01a1 ch\u1ebf ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc trong kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Trong b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng n\u00e0o, m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 t\u1eadp h\u1ee3p c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi tia t\u1eed ngo\u1ea1i\u00a0 &#8220;th\u1ee7 ph\u1ea1m&#8221; g\u00e2y ch\u00e1y n\u1eafng, s\u1ea1m da v\u00e0 l\u00e3o h\u00f3a s\u1edbm. Nh\u1eefng ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ea5p th\u1ee5, ph\u1ea3n chi\u1ebfu ho\u1eb7c l\u00e0m l\u1ec7ch h\u01b0\u1edbng tia UV \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba ch\u00fang x\u00e2m nh\u1eadp v\u00e0 ph\u00e1 h\u1ee7y c\u1ea5u tr\u00fac da.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4187\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4187\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4187\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/68-1.webp\" alt=\"C\u01a1 ch\u1ebf ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc trong kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/68-1.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/68-1-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/68-1-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/68-1-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4187\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">C\u01a1 ch\u1ebf ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc trong kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"hai-nhom-mang-loc-pho-bien-vat-ly-va-hoa-hoc\"><\/span><b>Hai nh\u00f3m m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn: V\u1eadt l\u00fd v\u00e0 H\u00f3a h\u1ecdc<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"1-mang-loc-vo-co-vat-ly\"><\/span><b><i>1. M\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc v\u00f4 c\u01a1 (v\u1eadt l\u00fd)<\/i><\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u00f2ng n\u00e0y th\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1ed3m Zinc Oxide v\u00e0 Titanium Dioxide \u2013 nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n kho\u00e1ng c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u1ea3n x\u1ea1 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp tia UV kh\u1ecfi b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t da. \u0110i\u1ec3m c\u1ed9ng l\u00e0 ch\u00fang kh\u00e1 l\u00e0nh t\u00ednh, \u00edt g\u00e2y k\u00edch \u1ee9ng v\u00e0 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p cho l\u00e0n da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m. Nh\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m duy nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i l\u1edbp tr\u1eafng nh\u1eb9 tr\u00ean da, tuy nhi\u00ean c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 h\u1ea1t nano hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4188\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4188\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4188\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/68-2.webp\" alt=\"M\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc v\u00f4 c\u01a1 (v\u1eadt l\u00fd)\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/68-2.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/68-2-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/68-2-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/68-2-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4188\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">M\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc v\u00f4 c\u01a1 (v\u1eadt l\u00fd)<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"2-mang-loc-huu-co-hoa-hoc\"><\/span><b><i>2. M\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc h\u1eefu c\u01a1 (h\u00f3a h\u1ecdc)<\/i><\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean c\u01a1 ch\u1ebf h\u1ea5p th\u1ee5 tia UV v\u00e0 chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed5i n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec7t v\u00f4 h\u1ea1i. M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u00e1i t\u00ean th\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ea5y l\u00e0 Octinoxate, Tinosorb S hay Uvinul A Plus. Ch\u00fang c\u00f3 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 cao trong vi\u1ec7c ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n tia UVA\/UVB v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u1eddng mang l\u1ea1i k\u1ebft c\u1ea5u m\u1ecfng nh\u1eb9, d\u1ec5 t\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec1u. Tuy nhi\u00ean, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 \u00fd th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 l\u00e0n da d\u1ec5 k\u00edch \u1ee9ng, v\u00e0 n\u00ean tr\u00e1nh c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t g\u00e2y tranh c\u00e3i nh\u01b0 Oxybenzone.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4189\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4189\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4189\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/68-3.webp\" alt=\"M\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc h\u1eefu c\u01a1 (h\u00f3a h\u1ecdc)\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/68-3.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/68-3-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/68-3-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/68-3-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4189\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">M\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc h\u1eefu c\u01a1 (h\u00f3a h\u1ecdc)<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"vai-tro-cua-mang-loc-trong-viec-bao-ve-lan-da\"><\/span><b>Vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc trong vi\u1ec7c b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 l\u00e0n da<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4191\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4191\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4191\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/68-5.webp\" alt=\"Vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc trong vi\u1ec7c b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 l\u00e0n da\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/68-5.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/68-5-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/68-5-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/68-5-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4191\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc trong vi\u1ec7c b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 l\u00e0n da<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"ngan-chan-tia-cuc-tim-tan-cong\"><\/span><b><i>Ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n tia c\u1ef1c t\u00edm t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng<\/i><\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Nh\u1edd v\u00e0o c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t c\u00f3 trong h\u1ec7 m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc, tia UVA \u2013 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y l\u00e3o h\u00f3a v\u00e0 UVB \u2013 t\u00e1c nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn da ch\u00e1y \u0111\u1ecf, s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1eef \u1edf b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i l\u1edbp bi\u1ec3u b\u00ec. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y gi\u00fap duy tr\u00ec l\u00e0n da \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u, kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 \u00edt b\u1ecb t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng do n\u1eafng g\u1eaft.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"tao-hang-rao-bao-ve-truoc-moi-truong-o-nhiem\"><\/span><b><i>T\u1ea1o h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u00f4 nhi\u1ec5m<\/i><\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 ng\u0103n UV, nhi\u1ec1u lo\u1ea1i m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc hi\u1ec7n nay c\u00f2n t\u00edch h\u1ee3p kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ed1ng \u00f4 nhi\u1ec5m v\u00e0 ch\u1ed1ng oxy h\u00f3a. Ch\u00fang h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh l\u1edbp m\u00e0ng m\u1ecfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da kh\u1ecfi b\u1ee5i m\u1ecbn, vi khu\u1ea9n v\u00e0 kim lo\u1ea1i n\u1eb7ng, nh\u1eefng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 \u0111ang ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn \u1edf m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"han-che-hien-tuong-chay-nang\"><\/span><b><i>H\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf hi\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u00e1y n\u1eafng<\/i><\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac v\u1edbi n\u1eafng m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1eeb c\u00e1c m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn da b\u1ecb r\u00e1t \u0111\u1ecf, s\u01b0ng nh\u1eb9 ho\u1eb7c th\u1eadm ch\u00ed bong tr\u00f3c. V\u1edbi h\u1ec7 m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc t\u1ed1t, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 y\u00ean t\u00e2m ra ngo\u00e0i v\u00e0o ban ng\u00e0y m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng lo da b\u1ecb t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng qu\u00e1 m\u1ee9c.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"lam-cham-qua-trinh-lao-hoa-da\"><\/span><b><i>L\u00e0m ch\u1eadm qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh l\u00e3o h\u00f3a da<\/i><\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u1ee3i \u00edch &#8220;th\u1ea7m l\u1eb7ng&#8221; nh\u01b0ng c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng ch\u1ee9a m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc t\u1ed1i \u01b0u l\u00e0 gi\u00fap l\u00e0m ch\u1eadm s\u1ef1 h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a n\u1ebfp nh\u0103n, \u0111\u1ed1m n\u00e2u v\u00e0 t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng m\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e0n h\u1ed3i da do \u00e1nh n\u1eafng l\u00e2u ng\u00e0y g\u00e2y ra.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"phu-hop-cho-su-dung-hang-ngay\"><\/span><b><i>Ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p cho s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng h\u1eb1ng ng\u00e0y<\/i><\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">V\u1edbi c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 c\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfn hi\u1ec7n nay, nhi\u1ec1u m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tinh ch\u1ec9nh \u0111\u1ec3 mang l\u1ea1i k\u1ebft c\u1ea5u m\u1ecfng nh\u1eb9, th\u1ea9m th\u1ea5u nhanh v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y nh\u1eddn r\u00edt. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y gi\u00fap ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 hay b\u00ed b\u00e1ch tr\u00ean da.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"loi-ket\"><\/span><b>L\u1eddi k\u1ebft<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ch\u1ecdn kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn k\u1ebft c\u1ea5u hay ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 SPF cao, m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng c\u00f3 trong s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 g\u00ec, thu\u1ed9c nh\u00f3m n\u00e0o v\u00e0 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi l\u00e0n da ra sao. Vi\u1ec7c hi\u1ec3u k\u1ef9 v\u1ec1 m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00fang s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m, m\u00e0 c\u00f2n gi\u00fap l\u00e0n da \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n v\u00e0 an to\u00e0n m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y\u00a0 d\u00f9 l\u00e0 \u1edf v\u0103n ph\u00f2ng, ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng hay khi du l\u1ecbch bi\u1ec3n.<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng &#8220;h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o&#8221; \u00e2m th\u1ea7m nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng thi\u1ebft y\u1ebfu. V\u1eady c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0y ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o? C\u00f3 bao nhi\u00eau lo\u1ea1i? V\u00e0 b\u1ea1n n\u00ean l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ra sao?<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":7,"featured_media":4192,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[16],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-4186","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-thong-tin-nganh"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4186","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection"